title: Belianske Tatry: Lakes of colours, an iconic dog and Mars
itunes:author: The Slovak Spectator
itunes:summary:
Spectacular Slovakia welcomes back Sergei (Russia) and Ingeborg (Norway), who live in Košice. This time, they will take listeners to the Belianske Tatry mountain range.  
 
Presenter: Peter Dlhopolec
